  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "A house rule is a change to a game's published or traditional [rules](./rules.md) adopted by a particular group of [players](./player.md). House rules are local: they apply at this table, in this group, for these sessions. They don't change the game in general; they change the game *as played here*.",
